ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T08:30:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>英文簡稱係乜，我女友都有個類似咁既名</blockquote><br />\nIBS</blockquote><br />\n佢就係ibs，雖然好易/成日肚痛，但好似未去到你咁誇wor, 仲成日食雪糕"},{"pid":"0f85136b7756cda9d39dd67fe95fe23bb2142fd1","tid":254360,"uid":482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T09:41:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去超市買四神粉飲呀 堅有效</blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打先，<br />\n病急亂投醫<br />\n睇專科醫生食藥食到傻"},{"pid":"690a4dadd52ccfbca9c5ba91e77bd0dc35e1c41b","tid":254360,"uid":482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T09:43:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無諗過可能係敏感問題所以個肚成日唔舒服阿?<br />\n<br />\n唔討厭的話試下木瓜嗰啲叫有天然酵素嘅食物對腸胃點都叫有幫助. 我而家枕住食穀物加啲蜜糖咁, 個肚都算聽話少少.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我應該係情緒引起<br />\n有食益生菌就每日都可以痾一條金黃色<br />\n一冇食就痾爛水又臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd113ea250ae05e72e34ba3c1784e506fecc268c","tid":254360,"uid":482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T09:44:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>英文簡稱係乜，我女友都有個類似咁既名</blockquote><br />\nIBS</blockquote><br />\n佢就係ibs，雖然好易/成日肚痛，但好似未去到你咁誇wor, 仲成日食雪糕</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 牛奶雪糕更加唔敢掂<br />\n一飲親奶連續痾幾次水"},{"pid":"a7809636134f5de034a313a11d12c619b173daac","tid":254360,"uid":60020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T09:57:40.000Z","msg":"腸易激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a516cd1b07b0e053160f719cff922f23947fada","tid":254360,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T10:00:59.000Z","msg":"想問下會唔會好易肚痛"},{"pid":"a9fa0602707c213c76cb4ac74060678bf3273e17","tid":254360,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T10:04:02.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日失驚無神肚痛肚痾"},{"pid":"89b286e0b5751a4e854b89643cd54d9e6832b056","tid":254360,"uid":37530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T10:07:47.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲個肚會響？<br />\n唔係肚餓都會響<br />\n好鬼大聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18451ad67195f1a4b45d1d7874de53ae2e37eed9","tid":254360,"uid":64378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T10:09:38.000Z","msg":"以前個fd 有，幫佢做過research,<br />\n<br />\n食藥之外其實hypnosis 都有效<br />\n<br />\n你地可以去poly lib 搵irritable bowel syndrome, 得一兩本講 hypnosis and ibs"},{"pid":"bdeffd0a038eadd26181be75cfe89d678d3ce08d","tid":254360,"uid":482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T10:18:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下會唔會好易肚痛</blockquote><br />\n都會好易<br />\n一痛就要馬上去廁所<br />\n超過半小時車都唔敢搭"},{"pid":"82eeeb0f0e051b053a83ef2056e8f6e278a38d77","tid":254360,"uid":85431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T10:19:51.000Z","msg":"我有，逢hea就會發作"}]}